 <text id="F6067T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>William Hoke requests that George Brewer tend to his financial affairs. Hoke wants Brewer to
     look into a claim for losses caused by the Confederates. He asks that Brewer send him a blanket
     out of the proceeds.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
   

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1868-03-02">March 2, 1868</date>
      <name type="place">Waldo Marin <abbr expan="County">Co</abbr> Ohio</name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><abbr expan="Mr.">M</abbr>
      <orig reg="George">gorge</orig> W <orig reg="Brewer">Bruer</orig></salute>
    </opener>

    <p>I see it in the <orig reg="valley">valy</orig> spirit that <orig reg="they">thea</orig> are
      <orig reg="making">maken</orig> a <orig reg="move">muve</orig> to pay for our <orig reg="loss"
      >loes</orig> by the rebels now <orig reg="friend">frend</orig>
     <orig reg="George">gorge</orig> tend to mine I <orig reg="don't">dont</orig>
     <orig reg="know">no</orig> what my <orig reg="amount">ammounte</orig> was <orig reg="anymore"
      >any more</orig> you <orig reg="have">hav</orig> it send me a <orig reg="blanket"
     >blanke</orig> of my <orig reg="amount">a mounte</orig> and I <orig reg="lost">loste</orig> a
     bay horse the time <orig reg="Imboden">emboden</orig> army <orig reg="lay">la</orig> at the
     cove <orig reg="gap">gape</orig> the time of the move from <orig reg="there">thare</orig> to
     the <orig reg="fight">fite</orig> at <orig reg="Gettysburg">getisburg</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fr</orig> my boys had the horses on the mountain above <orig
      reg="McConnellsburg">maconelsburg</orig> now I <orig reg="want">wonte</orig> to <orig
      reg="know">no</orig>
     <orig reg="whether">wether</orig> I <orig reg="must">muste</orig> prove him and send it to you
     he was coke in 1863 as near as I <orig reg="can">cin</orig>
     <orig reg="tell">tel</orig> from the 20 of june <abbr expan="until">til</abbr> the <orig
      reg="first">firste</orig>of July <orig reg="write">rite</orig> to me and <orig reg="let"
     >lete</orig> me <orig reg="know">no</orig>
     <orig reg="all">al</orig>
     <orig reg="about">aboute</orig> it my <orig reg="address">a dres</orig> is Waldo Marin. <abbr
      expan="County">Co.</abbr> Ohio</p>

    <closer>
     <salute>I remain yours <orig reg="truly">truley</orig></salute>
     <signed><abbr expan="William">W<hi rend="super">m</hi></abbr> Hoke</signed>
     <seg type="postscript">on when I <orig reg="got">gote</orig> up this morning it was <orig
       reg="snowing">snoen</orig> and this is a bad day send me a <orig reg="blanket">blanke</orig>
      of my <orig reg="claim">clam</orig> and I <orig reg="will">wil</orig> send you the <orig
       reg="prices">prics</orig> of my other horse and then I <orig reg="will">wil</orig> make you a
       <orig reg="offer">ofer</orig> for my <orig reg="claim">clame</orig> if you cash it we are all
       <orig reg="well">wel</orig> and hope you <orig reg="are">ar</orig>
      <orig reg="enjoying">engoyen</orig> the same give my <orig reg="best">beste</orig>
      <orig reg="respect">respecte</orig> to daniel trosle nothing more at this time <orig
       reg="write">rite</orig>
      <orig reg="soon">son</orig> and <orig reg="let">lete</orig> me <orig reg="know">no</orig> all
       <orig reg="about">a boute</orig> it</seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
 </text>
